WEBVTT

00:00.066 --> 00:02.728
ï»¿One of the world's most famous gorillas has died.

00:02.830 --> 00:05.155
Koko was known for her ability to sign.

00:05.252 --> 00:08.757
She was born at the San Francisco Zoo in 1971.

00:08.983 --> 00:13.020
She moved to the Gorilla Foundation in the Santa Cruz Mountains in 1974.

00:13.359 --> 00:15.601
Her ability to communicate captured hearts.

00:15.837 --> 00:18.759
Koko appeared on the cover of National Geographic twice.

00:18.979 --> 00:23.573
Her full name is Hanabiko, Japanese for "fireworks child."

